---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
import { sbtiTypes } from "../data/sbti-types";
---

<SiteLayout
    title="SBTI 人格测试 | 深度性格解码与灵魂侧写 - 官方入口"
    description="最火爆的SBTI人格测试，通过24个核心维度解析你的内在性格标签。比MBTI更真实，更具冲击力的性格实验。"
>
    <style>
        :root {
            --main-bg: #ffffff;
            --accent: #00ff66;
            --black: #000000;
        }
        body {
            font-family: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--main-bg);
            color: var(--black);
        }
        .neo-brutal {
            border: 3px solid var(--black);
            box-shadow: 5px 5px 0px 0px var(--black);
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .neo-brutal:hover {
            transform: translate(-2px, -2px);
            box-shadow: 7px 7px 0px 0px var(--black);
        }
        .heading-font {
            font-family: "Archivo Black", sans-serif;
        }
        .gallery-card-image {
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--black);
        }
        .gallery-intro {
            display: -webkit-box;
            -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
    </style>
    <div class="selection:bg-black selection:text-white">
        <header
            class="max-w-5xl mx-auto py-6 px-4 flex justify-between items-center"
        >
            <a
                href="/"
                class="heading-font text-3xl tracking-tighter border-b-4 border-black"
                aria-label="返回首页"
            >
                MySBTI.Fun
            </a>
            <nav class="space-x-6 font-bold text-sm uppercase hidden md:block">
                <a href="#about" class="hover:line-through">关于</a>
                <a href="#gallery" class="hover:line-through">画廊</a>
                <a href="#faq" class="hover:line-through">常见问题</a>
                <a
                    href="/test/"
                    class="bg-black text-white px-4 py-2 neo-brutal">开始测试</a
                >
            </nav>
        </header>

        <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 text-center">
            <h1
                class="heading-font text-5xl md:text-8xl mb-6 uppercase leading-none"
            >
                <span class="line-through">MBTI已经过时</span>
                <br />
                <span class="bg-[#00FF66] px-4">SBTI来了！</span>
            </h1>
            <p
                class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 text-gray-800"
            >
                SBTI
                是基于行为逻辑的性格重构测试。不提供虚伪的赞美，只揭示最真实的人格底色。
            </p>
            <div
                id="start"
                class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center"
            >
                <a
                    href="/test/"
                    class="bg-[#00FF66] text-black heading-font text-2xl py-6 px-12 neo-brutal w-full md:w-auto inline-flex justify-center"
                >
                    立即进入测试
                </a>
                <span
                    class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 underline underline-offset-4"
                    >耗时约 5 分钟 / 免费</span
                >
            </div>
        </main>

        <section
            id="about"
            class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6"
        >
            <div class="bg-white p-6 neo-brutal border-blue-500">
                <h3 class="heading-font text-xl mb-2">01. 猛猛开算</h3>
                <p class="text-sm">不讲废话，先把你的灵魂拆成 24 块再说。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 neo-brutal border-purple-500">
                <h3 class="heading-font text-xl mb-2">02. 颜值侧写</h3>
                <p class="text-sm">
                    结果不是报告，是一张看起来很会发疯的性格海报。
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 neo-brutal border-yellow-500">
                <h3 class="heading-font text-xl mb-2">03. 不问身份</h3>
                <p class="text-sm">不记你是谁，只记你有多离谱。</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="gallery" class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-20">
            <div
                class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between gap-6 mb-10 text-left"
            >
                <div>
                    <p
                        class="font-black uppercase text-sm tracking-[0.25em] text-gray-500 mb-3"
                    >
                        SBTI Gallery
                    </p>
                    <h2 class="heading-font text-4xl md:text-6xl leading-none">
                        sbti 画廊
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <p
                    class="max-w-xl text-base md:text-lg font-medium text-gray-700"
                >
                    全部SBTI人格海报都放在这里。先看脸
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-5">
                {
                    sbtiTypes.map((type) => (
                        <a
                            href={`/gallery/${type.slug}/`}
                            class="group bg-white neo-brutal overflow-hidden text-left"
                        >
                            <div class="aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden gallery-card-image">
                                <img
                                    src={type.image}
                                    alt={`${type.code} ${type.cn}`}
                                    class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-[1.03] transition-transform duration-200"
                                    loading="lazy"
                                />
                            </div>
                            <div class="p-4">
                                <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
                                    <div>
                                        <h3 class="heading-font text-2xl leading-none break-words">
                                            {type.code}
                                        </h3>
                                        <p class="mt-1 font-bold text-sm text-gray-700">
                                            {type.cn}
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                    <span class="text-xs font-black uppercase border-2 border-black px-2 py-1">
                                        详情
                                    </span>
                                </div>
                                <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-700 gallery-intro">
                                    {type.intro}
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </a>
                    ))
                }
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="faq" class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-20">
            <h2
                class="heading-font text-4xl mb-10 text-center underline decoration-[#00FF66]"
            >
                F.A.Q.
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <details
                    class="group bg-white border-2 border-black p-4 open:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"
                >
                    <summary
                        class="list-none font-black text-lg cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center"
                    >
                        什么是 SBTI 人格测试？
                        <span class="group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform"
                            >+</span
                        >
                    </summary>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                        比 MBTI 更丰富更符合当代宝宝的人格测试！
                    </p>
                </details>

                <details
                    class="group bg-white border-2 border-black p-4 open:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"
                >
                    <summary
                        class="list-none font-black text-lg cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center"
                    >
                        SBTI人格测试结果准确吗？
                        <span class="group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform"
                            >+</span
                        >
                    </summary>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Maybe！</p>
                </details>

                <details
                    class="group bg-white border-2 border-black p-4 open:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"
                >
                    <summary
                        class="list-none font-black text-lg cursor-pointer flex justify-between items-center"
                    >
                        如何分享我的 SBTI 报告？
                        <span class="group-open:rotate-45 transition-transform"
                            >+</span
                        >
                    </summary>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                        宝宝。测试完成后，请直接在结果页面截图
                    </p>
                </details>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer class="bg-black text-white py-12 px-4 mt-10">
            <div
                class="max-w-5xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-8"
            >
                <div class="heading-font text-2xl uppercase">
                    mysbti.fun 2026
                </div>
                <div class="text-gray-400 text-xs text-center md:text-right">
                    <p>本测试仅供娱乐与自我探索，不构成任何医疗或职业建议。</p>
                    <p class="mt-2">© 2026 mysbti.fun. NO RIGHTS RESERVED.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </div>
</SiteLayout>
